When we go for two pointer Concept.

When you read a problem, ask these:
Step-by-step thinking:
❓ Is the array sorted?
→ YES → Try two pointers immediately
❓ Do I need pair/triplet?
→ YES → Two pointers likely
❓ Can I reduce nested loops?
→ YES → Replace O(n²) with two pointers
❓ Am I comparing from both ends?
→ YES → Two pointers
❓ Is it about subarray/substring?
→ YES → Sliding window (two pointers)
